Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:03:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where they instigated an all-out war \Nagainst the New Fish-Man Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally defeated \NHordy in a fierce fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thwarted his plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Spread the sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me out for a fun stroll again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to a real forest above ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we pass through this deep sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll get to the ultimate sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To the New World! Heading \Nfor the Ultimate Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After leaving the Fish-Man Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ship ascends toward the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's going very well!\N--Yeah, almost too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:05:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get hungry. Let's do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until I finish making this, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Shower Tempo. \NDo you wanna use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. I just brushed myself 2 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, doesn't that \Ncloud look like cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? It's not sweet, sweet cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There is something sweet \Nand yummy in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Looks pretty sweet and yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, please! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, step away from the cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary!  I don't wanna \Neat that cloud anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so relaxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first bath on the Sunny in 2 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so luxurious with a view of the deep \Nsea - it's as beautiful as the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they need you on the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll go up before \Nwe ride an upward current.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a sea monster strikes, \Nthey can take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want a giant fish so \Nthe ropes gotta be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I think this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You guys are having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't even thought about it \Non our way to the Fish-Man Island
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I was excited to see the island
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we catch a deep-sea fish \Nnow, Sanji can cook it for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it'll go with cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cook, huh? That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to have a drink in \Ncelebration of entering the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, which one should we catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want something that looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one would taste good \Nfried up with some salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fried fish with salt sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about slicing it in half and grilling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like an eel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That one looks good too! It \Nwould be yummy with some mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't look good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you cook \Nit, it won't taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? Well, whatever's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sanji can cook up any fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you wanted that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't it a little too big?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry! Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack - Capture Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a deep-sea fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's a fish? \NLooks like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, not again! They keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reel it in already, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, I can't! The \Nship is gonna flip over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! Is it a Russian doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is shaking and  I \Nhear them yelling on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have trusted them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style - 360 Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Sanji, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A deep-sea fish, huh? Can't wait to cook it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first of all, how did you get burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this! You won't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 2 more fish inside that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is the ship really moving forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we're sinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant sea snake! No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, get closer! Let's eat that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have too much to carry already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't tell me it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitestrom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant whirlpool that appears \Nout of the blue in the deep sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like a living dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whirlpool in the deep sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?! This \Nis dangerous, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, those fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Oh no! It must be the Whitestrom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a ship gets caught up in the whirlpool,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll end up somewhere far \Noff usually missing its crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That means the crew \Nall died, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dangerous! Let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship will end up somewhere far off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like the wormhole of my dreams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We have to get away \Nfrom that whirlpool now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Our navigator's back! Let's go, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! What is that fish doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?! We \Ncan't advance if we're pulling that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? The fish got caught in the whirlpool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No! Get it back!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We're gonna cut it loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We wanted to eat the deep-sea fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important to \Nyou - the fish or your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you get in this much trouble \Nwhile I was away for only 10 minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, Coup de Burst?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's super too late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Stop "Huh?"-ing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get caught in the whirlpool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's too late!\N--I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold onto the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is super not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Sunny can't endure \Na whirlpool this wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I blame Luffy and the rest of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head is spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we get out of the whirlpool somehow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no records of someone \Nescaping the Whitestrom! Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has ever survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of the New World, \Nwe're all going to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny was not destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hit something and got \Nbumped out of the whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this black wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like the Red Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fin? Don't tell me it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it singing. It must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's a pod of whales!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those scars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come back to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I come back, let's fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon! Wait for us! We'll come \Nback here for sure...! For sure!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon! You got so much bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! Laboon should be \Nin the first half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gigantic! He can't fit \Nthrough the hole in the Red Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a miracle to come \Nacross a pod of Island Whales.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them have scars like Laboon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the scars look the same! I can't \Nbelieve it! But it's not Laboon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up all of the crew! \NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon! Stop! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me from the Rumbar Pirates! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses! \NThat's a different whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not on a whale watching crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still dangerous out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me call the roll to make sure \Nno one got lost in the whirlpool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we gotta get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship will be destroyed if \Nthose giant whales crash into us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you call our names?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Six more of us \Nare alive and well here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we shouldn't do anything, \Nfools! Let's watch the whales now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're such giant whales, \Nthey're creating a current.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be dangerous to go against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tighten the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the ship in the direction \Nthat the whales are heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! This is where Laboon came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are any of you related to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone looking for a calf \Nwho got lost 50 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! He's doing okay \Non the other side of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Luffy-san, he's very big now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't worry! \NI think Laboon would...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch the stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stick with the whales for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:18:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo ho ho ho… Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo ho ho ho… Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up all of the crew! \NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea wind blows to where, who knows? \NThe waves will be our guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O'er across the ocean's tide, \Nthe sunset is goin' wild
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See the sky! Birds singing \Nin circles passing by!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bid farewell to weaver's town! \NSay so long to port renowned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing a song, it won't be long \Nbefore we're casting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross the gold and silver waves, \Nchangin' into water sprays!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing out on our journey \Nto the ends of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up all of the crew! \NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates we, we'll divide \Nand conquer all the seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the waves to rest our heads, \Nship beneath us as our bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoisted high up on the mast \Nour Jolly Roger flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in the endless sky, \Na storm has started comin' by!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Waves are dancing having fun, \Nit's time to sound the drums!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're giving us a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If we let blow winds of fear, \Nthen the end of us is near!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him take us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're gonna go upward too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, tomor-row the sun will rise again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo ho ho ho… Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo ho ho ho… Yo ho ho ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the New World, the final sea \Nof the Grand Line, up above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:20:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10, 9, 8, 7, 6...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...5, 4, 3, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...1!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're out!\N--In the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We did it!\N--We finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not time to celebrate yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the whales!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll tell Laboon about \Nyou all if we see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon's relatives! Take care of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had heard about it but \Nit's more than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…really bad weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is filled with thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is very rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The needle is going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see some ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are having a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, those are warships!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't ask for anything better!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats finally \Nmake it to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They encounter many grueling trials...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...including a mysterious girl small \Nenough to fit in the palm of you hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it also brings to light a conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...between pirates and the \NNavy of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Z's Ambition! \NLily the Little Giant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
